OL,3,CWarning from farmer who almost lost
OL,4,Cleg after insect bite
OL,6,FA farmer who almost lost a leg after
OL,7,Fbeing bitten by an insect is warning
OL,8,Fothers to be aware of the signs of
OL,9,Fsepsis.
OL,11,FSimon Clayton developed an infection
OL,12,Fwhich caused severe swelling and
OL,13,Fredness after being bitten on his farm
OL,14,Fin Lincolnshire in February.
OL,16,FHe said he felt his body "shutting
OL,17,Fdown" and was taken to hospital, where
OL,18,Fhe was told he may lose the limb.
