OL,3,CWarning from farmer who almost lost
OL,4,Cleg after insect bite
OL,6,FHe said he remembers a doctor telling
OL,7,Fhim: "I have to tell you - you are
OL,8,Fvery seriously ill. There is a chance
OL,9,Fyou could lose your leg. It could end
OL,10,Fhere, that could be it."
OL,12,FMr Clayton had been harvesting sugar
OL,13,Fbeet when he believes he suffered the
OL,14,Fbite.
OL,16,FA day later his leg started to swell
OL,17,Fand he felt unwell.
OL,19,FHe was given antibiotics, but his
OL,20,Fcondition continued to worsen.
