OL,3,CWarning from farmer who almost lost
OL,4,Cleg after insect bite
OL,6,F"I was quite a mess," he said. "(My
OL,7,Fleg) was swollen, from my toe to my
OL,8,Fgroin. I was shaking I was shivering,
OL,9,FI was hot I was cold. I hadn't been to
OL,10,Fthe toilet for two days."
OL,12,FHe saw a doctor who told him the
OL,13,Finfection could affect his heart.
OL,15,F"The symptoms were characteristic of
OL,16,Fsepsis - I was hot, I was cold, I
OL,17,Fwasn't eating or drinking that much
OL,18,Fand I was a little delirious."
