OL,4,Cleg after insect bite
OL,6,FSepsis is a type of blood poisoning
OL,7,Fthat occurs when the immune system
OL,8,Freacts to an infection. It attacks
OL,9,Forgans and tissues within the body. If
OL,10,Fnot treated immediately, it can result
OL,11,Fin organ failure and death.
OL,13,FMr Clayton's brother, Mark, said it
OL,14,Fwas a frightening time.
OL,16,FHe said: "It shook the whole family
OL,17,Freally, I was pleased I was there to
OL,18,Fbe there for him while he got on the
OL,19,Froad to recovery."
