OL,3,CWarning from farmer who almost lost
OL,4,Cleg after insect bite
OL,6,FIntensive care consultant Dr Ron
OL,7,FDaniels, of the UK Sepsis Trust, said
OL,8,Fone in five people who develop sepsis
OL,9,Fdo not survive.
OL,11,FHe added: "Even among survivors there
OL,12,Fcan be life changing consequences.
OL,13,FThat might include amputation, but it
OL,14,Fcan certainly include psychological
OL,15,Fafter effects and physical after
OL,16,Feffects like really bad fatigue and
OL,17,Fpain syndromes.
