OL,3,CWarning from farmer who almost lost
OL,4,Cleg after insect bite
OL,6,F"Sepsis accounts for about 48,000
OL,7,Flives lost in the UK every year.
OL,8,FThat's more lives than are lost to
OL,9,Fbreast, bowel and prostate cancer put
OL,10,Ftogether. So sepsis can be deadly, but
OL,11,Fthe good news is if we spot it early
OL,12,Fit can usually be treated."
